recommend it though, as if you're really jonesing for it, you'll likely buy it anyway, but if you're semi-interested for a time killer - don't do it, as you could be making headaches for your computer.As it is, it has gotten bad enough for me that I've uninstalled it. So, buyer beware if you decide to go for it."
